# Description:
# Try to find Coin library. Try first to see if Coin3D-3 is available. If not,
# check for Coin3D-2.
# Once run this will define: 
#
# COIN3D_FOUND
# COIN3D_LIBRARIES
# COIN3D_INCLUDE_DIRS
